    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> cider vinegar</strong>, 2 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tsp]</span><strong> sugar</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[3 tbsp]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a large bowl and stir it all together</p><p>Add the <strong>grated carrot </strong>to the bowl and set aside to pickle – this is your <strong>quick-pickled carrot</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-27-1712749503474-x200.jpg",
