            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the<strong> </strong>kofte are cooking, add your<strong> natural yoghurt</strong> to a small bowl with your <strong>ground</strong> <strong>sumac</strong>, <strong>remaining grated garlic</strong> (not a big garlic fan? Try using less!), a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a<strong> </strong>pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Stir it all together – this is your<strong> sumac yoghurt</strong></p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper and shred finely</p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>finely into rounds, then cut in half</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
